{"type":"message","id":"1526a9b6","parentId":"50801828","timestamp":"2026-05-09T09:44:58.981Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me analyze the timeout issue with the \"Cron Governor 每5分鐘系統監控\" job (id: 8ecf6a44-2c50-4d77-b645-e226ac1a976d).\n\nLooking at the job details:\n- Schedule: every 3600000ms (1 hour) - but description says \"每5分鐘系統監控\" and \"20分鐘→60分鐘\"\n- Last duration: 60563ms (60.5 seconds)\n- Timeout set in payload: 60 seconds\n- Error: \"cron: job execution timed out\"\n\n\n- The execution is consistently hitting the 60-second timeout, with consecutive errors showing it's been failing this way repeatedly. The Python script runs fine in isolation and completes in about 60 seconds, but the cron job is set to trigger every hour with a 60-second timeout—which means there's almost no buffer. The description mentions a schedule change from 20 minutes to 60 minutes, but the actual interval appears to still be set to an hour, creating a mismatch between what should happen and what's configured. Looking at the consecutive errors more closely, the issue is that the Python script is consistently timing out at around 60 seconds when it runs as a cron job, even though it should complete faster. The timeout value in the payload matches this exactly, so when the system kills the process at the 60-second mark, it's barely exceeding the limit. I should increase the timeout to give the script more breathing room. increase to 90 seconds and investigate why the script is timing out when called from the agent environment but runs fine standalone. Looking at the script path, it appears to be executing cron governor monitoring with explicit 60-second timeouts that are being hit consistently. The solution is straightforward: bump the timeout up to 90 seconds to give it breathing room, and I should also verify whether the \"每5分鐘\" in the name matches the actual 60-minute interval in the schedule.","thinkingSignature":"8c4a031a88e8e8b172bb13aa21dda0d833c6102a3b50ae10523021e67809c76d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_50ir082j050b_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls \"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\stores\\cron_governor.py\" 2>$null; echo \"EXIT:$LASTEXITCODE\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":22968,"output":466,"cacheRead":15104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38538,"cost":{"input":0.0068904,"output":0.0005591999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0009062399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00835584}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778319889231,"responseId":"064e3512c4652709a67cd39019edb5c0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"558217ee","parentId":"1526a9b6","timestamp":"2026-05-09T09:44:59.196Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_50ir082j050b_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"目錄: C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\stores\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\n-a----        2026/5/8  下午 07:59           8861 cron_governor.py                                                     \r\nEXIT:"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":203,"aggregated":"目錄: C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\stores\r\n\r\n\r\nMode                 LastWriteTime         Length Name                                                                 \r\n----                 -------------         ------ ----                                                                 \r\n-a----        2026/5/8  下午 07:59           8861 cron_governor.py                                                     \r\nEXIT:","cwd":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778319899196}}
{"type":"message","id":"6b16984a","parentId":"558217ee","timestamp":"2026-05-09T09:45:01.307Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The file exists. Let me check what it does and why it might be timing out.\n","thinkingSignature":"1902396f0264b52ae9ca858513d161e3b2250b89620e495ed95264f38420c86a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ibk58zk7xom5_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\stores\\cron_governor.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":167,"output":65,"cacheRead":38048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38280,"cost":{"input":0.0000501,"output":0.000078,"cacheRead":0.0022828799999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0024109799999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778319899197,"responseId":"064e351cc39c3f86e24fb7ccea323bd0"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a19859f0","parentId":"6b16984a","timestamp":"2026-05-09T09:45:01.313Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ibk58zk7xom5_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\nCron Governor — 系統活動感知智能排程器\n=====================================\n職責：\n1. 每5分鐘評估系統活動分數（0-100）\n2. 低活動時段自動喚醒 cron jobs\n3. 高負載時抑制非緊急 jobs\n4. 保護 Gateway 資源，防止連鎖崩潰\n\n活動分數計算：\n- eventLoopDelayMaxMs: <500ms = 100分, >3000ms = 0分\n- CPU: <30% = 100分, >80% = 0分\n- Memory: <50% = 100分, >85% = 0分\n- cronQueueDepth: 0 = 100分, >5 = 0分\n- activeJobs: 0 = 100分, >3 = 0分\n\nThreshold:\n- <30分：進入「清醒時段」，允許高優先級 jobs\n- 30-60分：普通模式，按原排程\n- >60分：進入「節能模式」，只允許必要 jobs\n\"\"\"\n\nimport sys, json, time, psutil, os\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom urllib.request import urlopen, Request\n\nsys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')\n\nBASE_DIR = Path(r'C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System')\nSTORES_DIR = BASE_DIR / 'stores'\nSTATE_FILE = STORES_DIR / 'cron_governor_state.json'\nLOG_FILE = STORES_DIR / 'cron_governor_log.json'\n\n# ─── Config ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nGATEWAY_URL = 'http://127.0.0.1:18789'\nACTIVITY_THRESHOLD_LOW = 30      # 分數 < 30 → 清醒時段\nACTIVITY_THRESHOLD_HIGH = 60     # 分數 > 60 → 節能模式\nCHECK_INTERVAL_SEC = 1200       # 每20分鐘檢查一次\nWINDOW_START = 2   # 凌晨2:00（系統最空）\nWINDOW_END = 6     # 凌晨6:00（系統最空）\nMARKET_OPEN_HOUR = 9\nMARKET_CLOSE_HOUR = 16\n\n# ─── Helpers ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\ndef load_json(filepath, default=None):\n    if filepath.exists():\n        with open(filepath, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n            return json.load(f)\n    return default if default is not None else {}\n\ndef save_json(filepath, data):\n    with open(filepath, 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        json.dump(data, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n\ndef get_system_metrics():\n    \"\"\"抓取系統指標\"\"\"\n    metrics = {\n        'cpu_percent': 0,\n        'memory_percent': 0,\n        'event_loop_delay_ms': 0,\n        'cron_queue_depth': 0,\n        'active_jobs': 0,\n        'timestamp': datetime.now().isoformat()\n    }\n\n    # CPU / Memory via psutil\n    try:\n        metrics['cpu_percent'] = psutil.cpu_percent(interval=1)\n        vm = psutil.virtual_memory()\n        metrics['memory_percent'] = vm.percent\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f'psutil error: {e}')\n\n    # Parse gateway log for event loop delay\n    try:\n        log_path = Path(os.environ.get('TEMP', '/tmp')) / 'openclaw' / 'openclaw-2026-05-08.log'\n        if log_path.exists():\n            lines = log_path.read_text(encoding='utf-8', errors='ignore').splitlines()\n            for line in reversed(lines[-200:]):\n                try:\n                    entry = json.loads(line)\n                    msg = entry.get('message', '')\n                    if 'eventLoopDelayMaxMs' in msg or 'eventLoop' in msg:\n                        # Try to extract number\n                        import re\n                        m = re.search(r'eventLoopDelayMaxMs[\":\\s]+(\\d+)', msg)\n                        if m:\n                            metrics['event_loop_delay_ms'] = int(m.group(1))\n                            break\n                except:\n                    pass\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f'log parse error: {e}')\n\n    # Gateway API health check (as proxy for active jobs)\n    try:\n        req = Request(f'{GATEWAY_URL}/api/health', timeout=3)\n        # Just check if gateway is responsive\n        with urlopen(req, timeout=3) as resp:\n            pass\n        metrics['gateway_ok'] = True\n    except:\n        metrics['gateway_ok'] = False\n\n    return metrics\n\ndef calc_activity_score(metrics):\n    \"\"\"\n    計算系統活動分數（0-100）\n    100 = 完全空閒，0 = 完全過載\n    \"\"\"\n    scores = []\n\n    # CPU: 30% 以下 = 100分, 80% 以上 = 0分\n    cpu = metrics.get('cpu_percent', 0)\n    cpu_score = max(0, min(100, 100 - (cpu - 30) * (100/50))) if cpu >= 30 else 100\n    scores.append(('cpu', cpu_score, 0.25))\n\n    # Memory: 50% 以下 = 100分, 85% 以上 = 0分\n    mem = metrics.get('memory_percent', 0)\n    mem_score = max(0, min(100, 100 - (mem - 50) * (100/35))) if mem >= 50 else 100\n    scores.append(('memory', mem_score, 0.20))\n\n    # Event Loop Delay: <500ms = 100分, >3000ms = 0分\n    eld = metrics.get('event_loop_delay_ms', 0)\n    eld_score = max(0, min(100, 100 - (eld - 500) * (100/2500))) if eld >= 500 else 100\n    scores.append(('event_loop', eld_score, 0.35))\n\n    # Gateway responsiveness: OK = 100, Down = 0\n    gw_ok = metrics.get('gateway_ok', True)\n    scores.append(('gateway', 100 if gw_ok else 0, 0.20))\n\n    # Weighted average\n    total_score = sum(s[1] * s[2] for s in scores)\n    return int(total_score)\n\ndef get_window_mode():\n    \"\"\"判断當前是否在低活動時段窗口\"\"\"\n    now = datetime.now()\n    hour = now.hour\n    \n    # 凌晨低活動窗口\n    if WINDOW_START <= hour < WINDOW_END:\n        return 'deep_sleep'  # 深夜窗口，最寬鬆\n    \n    # 市場關閉後（16:00-02:00）\n    if hour >= MARKET_CLOSE_HOUR or hour < WINDOW_START:\n        return 'evening'     # 晚間窗口，中等寬鬆\n    \n    # 市場開放時間（09:00-16:00）\n    if MARKET_OPEN_HOUR <= hour < MARKET_CLOSE_HOUR:\n        return 'market_hours'  # 市場時間，最嚴格\n    \n    # 早盤或午餐時間\n    return 'normal'\n\ndef decide_action(score, window_mode, pending_jobs):\n    \"\"\"\n    根據分數和窗口模式決定允許動作\n    返回: (allow_new_jobs, max_concurrent, suppress_low_priority)\n    \"\"\"\n    # 清廉政（深夜）: 寬鬆\n    if window_mode == 'deep_sleep':\n        return True, 5, False\n    \n    # 晚間：適中\n    if window_mode == 'evening':\n        if score < 30:\n            return True, 3, False\n        elif score < 50:\n            return True, 2, True   # 抑制低優先級\n        else:\n            return False, 1, True   # 只允許風控\n    \n    # 市場時間：嚴格\n    if window_mode == 'market_hours':\n        if score < 20:\n            return True, 2, True\n        else:\n            return False, 1, True   # 只允許風控\n    \n    # 正常時間\n    if score < 30:\n        return True, 2, False\n    elif score < 50:\n        return True, 1, True\n    else:\n        return False, 1, True\n\ndef log_decision(score, window_mode, action, pending):\n    \"\"\"寫入決策日誌\"\"\"\n    log = load_json(LOG_FILE, [])\n    log.append({\n        'timestamp': datetime.now().isoformat(),\n        'activity_score': score,\n        'window_mode': window_mode,\n        'action': action,\n        'pending_jobs': pending,\n        'cpu': psutil.cpu_percent(interval=0.5),\n        'memory_percent': psutil.virtual_memory().percent\n    })\n    # Keep last 100 entries\n    if len(log) > 100:\n        log = log[-100:]\n    save_json(LOG_FILE, log)\n\n# ─── Main ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\ndef main():\n    print(f'=== Cron Governor | {datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M\")} ===')\n    \n    # 1. 抓取指標\n    metrics = get_system_metrics()\n    print(f'Metrics: CPU={metrics[\"cpu_percent\"]:.1f}% MEM={metrics[\"memory_percent\"]:.1f}% EL={metrics[\"event_loop_delay_ms\"]}ms GW={metrics[\"gateway_ok\"]}')\n    \n    # 2. 計算分數\n    score = calc_activity_score(metrics)\n    window = get_window_mode()\n    print(f'Score: {score}/100 | Window: {window}')\n    \n    # 3. 載入狀態\n    state = load_json(STATE_FILE, {'last_action': None, 'last_score': 50})\n    \n    # 4. 決策\n    allow_jobs, max_concurrent, suppress_low = decide_action(score, window, state.get('pending_jobs', 0))\n    \n    print(f'Action: allow={allow_jobs} max_concurrent={max_concurrent} suppress_low={suppress_low}')\n    \n    # 5. 更新狀態\n    state['activity_score'] = score\n    state['window_mode'] = window\n    state['last_check'] = datetime.now().isoformat()\n    state['allow_new_jobs'] = allow_jobs\n    state['max_concurrent'] = max_concurrent\n    state['suppress_low_priority'] = suppress_low\n    state['metrics'] = metrics\n    save_json(STATE_FILE, state)\n    \n    # 6. 日誌\n    action_str = f'allow={allow_jobs}|max={max_concurrent}|suppress={suppress_low}'\n    log_decision(score, window, action_str, state.get('pending_jobs', 0))\n    \n    print(f'State saved: {STATE_FILE}')\n    print(f'GOVERNOR DONE')\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    main()"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1778319901313}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ab19994","parentId":"a19859f0","timestamp":"2026-05-09T09:45:15.035Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The cron job for \"Cron Governor 每5分鐘系統監控\" timed out. Looking at the script, I can see several potential issues:\n\n1. **The script has `psutil.cpu_percent(interval=1)`** - This blocks for 1 second\n2. **The script has another `psutil.cpu_percent(interval=0.5)`** in `log_decision`\n3. **The log parsing logic** reads log files, which could be slow\n4. **The gateway API health check** has a 3-second timeout\n\nThe job's timeout is set to 60 seconds, but the `lastDurationMs` was 60563ms (60.5 seconds) - so it just barely timed out.\n\n\nThe real culprit is that `psutil.cpu_percent(interval=1)` call blocking for a full second, combined with the log file I/O and potential network latency on the gateway check. Since the job's timeout is already at 60 seconds and it exceeded that by just 0.5 seconds, I could bump it up to 90 seconds to give it more breathing room. Alternatively, I could reduce the blocking intervals in psutil to speed things up overall.","thinkingSignature":"2f538be375bc4f82a3f2a727e24959353a38ab018d522162073d39111102181d"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**問題診斷：**\n\nCron Governor 每5分鐘系統監控超時（60s exactly），原因：\n\n1. `psutil.cpu_percent(interval=1)` + `psutil.virtual_memory()` — 阻塞 1.5 秒\n2. 讀取 200 行日誌並做 JSON parsing\n3. Gateway API health check — 3 秒 timeout\n4. 整個 script 在 isolated session 起動還要經過 agent bootstrap\n\n60 秒 timeout 對這個任務太緊了（實際跑了 60.5s）。\n\n**修正方案：**\n\n1. **增加 timeout** 60s → 90s（最直接修復）\n2. **優化 script** — 減少 blocking interval、簡化日誌解析\n\n要我現在更新這個 job 的 timeout 嗎？還是先看過優化後的 script 再決定？\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_39oz0jsilavq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd \"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\stores\" && python -c \"import time; start=time.time(); import psutil; print(f'psutil load: {time.time()-start:.3f}s'); print(f'CPU: {psutil.cpu_p