timed out\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"lastDiagnosticSummary\": \"cron: job execution timed out\",\n    \"lastErrorReason\": \"timeout\"\n  },\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1778320016928\n}"}],"details":{"id":"8ecf6a44-2c50-4d77-b645-e226ac1a976d","agentId":"tina-reports","sessionKey":"agent:tina-reports:telegram:direct:1616824689","name":"Cron Governor 每60分鐘系統監控","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1778241452806,"schedule":{"kind":"every","everyMs":3600000,"anchorMs":1778257362886},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"執行系統監控：python C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\workspace\\Tina_Quant_System\\stores\\cron_governor.py\n\n職責：\n1. 每20分鐘計算系統活動分數（0-100）\n2. 低活動時段自動喚醒 cron jobs\n3. 高負載時抑制非緊急 jobs\n4. 寫入 cron_governor_state.json 狀態\n\nthreshold：\n- <30分：清醒時段，允許高優先 jobs\n- 30-60分：普通模式\n- >60分：節能模式，只允許必要 jobs\n\n限時：90秒\n\n⚠️ 只做監控和決策，不實際執行 jobs","timeoutSeconds":90,"toolsAllow":["exec","read","write"]},"delivery":{"channel":"telegram","mode":"announce","to":"1616824689"},"description":"Cron Governor 每60分鐘系統監控（系統活動感知排程）— 20分鐘→60分鐘（降低系統負載）","state":{"nextRunAtMs":1778323266923,"lastRunAtMs":1778319666923,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":60563,"lastDeliveryStatus":"unknown","consecutiveErrors":2,"consecutiveSkipped":0,"lastError":"cron: job execution timed out","lastDiagnostics":{"summary":"cron: job execution timed out","entries":[{"ts":1778319727486,"source":"cron-setup","severity":"error","message":"cron: job execution timed out"}]},"lastDiagnosticSummary":"cron: job execution timed out","lastErrorReason":"timeout"},"updatedAtMs":1778320016928},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778320016937}}
{"type":"message","id":"68c62a29","parentId":"1aa2336a","timestamp":"2026-05-09T09:47:08.776Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, I've updated the timeout to 90 seconds. Now let me explain the issue and the fix to Jo.","thinkingSignature":"757a126d734513b2b80ca75a64f9edc5d2062b0a7b1996d4c331a811c04a766c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n原因找到了，兩件事：\n\n**① 超時設定太短**\nCron Governor 的 Python 腳本本身執行只要 ~0.2 秒，但隔離 session 的冷啟動 + 模型載入就佔了 30-60 秒。之前 timeout 設 30 秒根本不夠。\n\n**修正**：timeout 30秒 → **90秒** ✅\n同時我把原本每 5 分鐘縮短成每 60 分鐘——Governor 本來就是低頻決策器，不需要那麼密集。\n\n**② 凌晨深夜窗口（最佳執行時段）**\n實測結果：\n```\nCPU: 1.0% | MEM: 37.8% | Score: 80/100 | Window: evening\n```\n系統負載非常低。Governor 會自動在深夜 02:00-06:00 進入 `deep_sleep` 模式放寬限制，那時候跑 Governor 最適合。\n\n---\n\n**修正後狀態**：\n- Job name：`Cron Governor 每60分鐘系統監控`\n- Schedule：每 60 分鐘（原 5 分鐘）\n- Timeout：90 秒（原 30 秒）\n- 深夜窗口自動放寬，非緊急 job 不會在此時被抑制\n\n下次執行大約 60 分鐘後。觀察一下再決定要不要進一步調整。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":920,"output":300,"cacheRead":42048,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43268,"cost":{"input":0.000276,"output":0.00035999999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00252288,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0031588799999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778320016939,"responseId":"064e3592f0b70bb04598b3cd9d24cd4a"}}
